# Netlify Redirects and Headers Configuration
# This file should be placed in the public folder

# Force HTTPS redirect
http://freeonlinetyping.com/*   https://freeonlinetyping.com/:splat   301!
http://www.freeonlinetyping.com/*   https://www.freeonlinetyping.com/:splat   301!

# Redirect www to non-www (canonical)
https://www.freeonlinetyping.com/*   https://freeonlinetyping.com/:splat   301!

# Force trailing slash removal (optional, for clean URLs)
https://freeonlinetyping.com/*/   https://freeonlinetyping.com/:splat   301!
